var e=`更新`,t=`Server`,n=`spacing`,r=`隨機`,i=`轉變`,a=`Size`,o=`day`,s=`hour`,c=`min`,l=`sec`,u=`Use`,d=`copied`,f=`copy`,p=`close`,m=`and`,h=`Resources`,g=`Solution`,_=`Providing`,v=`context`,y=`It`,b=`Introducing`,x=`variants`,S=`variables`,C=`Examples`,w=`已讀取`,T=`已跳過`,E=`截圖`,D=`提示詞`,O=`必需`,k=`架構`,A=`GitMCP`,j={Updates:e,"install-step-1":`將 daisyUI 作為 Node 套件安裝`,"install-step-2":`將 daisyUI 安裝為 Tailwind CSS 的外掛程式`,Server:t,"UI blocks":`UI blocks`,spacing:n,"available-on":`獲取管道`,"All radio inputs with the same name work together and only one of them can be open at a time. If you have more than one set of accordion items on a page, use different names for the radio inputs on each set.":`所有具相同名稱的單選按鈕將同時運作，並且一次只能開啟一個。如果您的頁面上有多個手風琴項目集合，請在每個集合中使用不同的單選按鈕名稱。`,"How to use daisyUI colors?":`如何使用 daisyUI 的色彩？`,"daisyUI is fully themeable and colorable,":`daisyUI 完全支援主題化和色彩化，`,"How to use daisyUI themes?":`如何使用 daisyUI 主題？`,Randomize:r,"try-online":`線上試試`,"2. Get daisyUI bundled JS file":`2.取得daisyUI捆綁的JS文件`,"Add daisyUI in your CSS file":`在 CSS 檔案中新增 daisyUI`,"noise background of the button if enabled":`Button 的雜訊背景（如果啟用）`,"2. Pikaday Calendar":`2.皮卡迪Calendar`,"Pikaday CDN Example":`Pikaday CDN 範例`,"Pikaday Svelte Example":`Pikaday Svelte 範例`,"Pikaday Vue Example":`Pikaday Vue 範例`,"Pikaday React Example":`Pikaday 反應範例`,"3. React Day Picker calendar":`3. React Day Picker Calendar`,"There are 3 methods to use modals":`有 3 種使用模態的方法`,"Method 2. checkbox":`方法2.Checkbox`,"Method 3. using anchor links":`方法3.使用錨鏈接`,"Follow [Tailwind CSS guide](https://tailwindcss.com/blog/standalone-cli) and get the latest version of Tailwind CSS executable.":`請按照 [Tailwind CSS 指南](https://tailwindcss.com/blog/standalone-cli) 並取得最新版本的 Tailwind CSS 執行檔。`,"If you are using a prefix for daisyUI, these CSS variables will be prefixed with that prefix as well. For example if prefix is `daisy-`, The  `--alert-color` CSS variable will be `--daisy-alert-color`.":"如果您使用 daisyUI 的前綴，這些 CSS variable 也會帶有該前綴。例如，如果前綴是 `daisy-`，則 `--alert-color` CSS variable 將是 `--daisy-alert-color`。","Here's how to use daisyUI llms.txt in your code editor:":`以下是在程式碼編輯器中使用 daisyUI llms.txt 的方法：`,"Copilot can generate daisyUI code for you.":`Copilot 可以為您產生 daisyUI 程式碼。`,"Add daisyUI's llms.txt file to your repo so that Copilot can use it by default.":`將 daisyUI 的 llms.txt 檔案新增至您的儲存庫中，以便 Copilot 可以透過 Default 使用它。`,"Run this command to save the llms.txt file to `.vscode/daisyui.md`":"執行此命令將 llms.txt 檔案儲存到 `.vscode/daisyui.md`","In `.vscode/settings.json` Add this:":"在 `.vscode/settings.json` 中加入以下內容：","Now in chat window you can type `@daisyui` to provide daisyUI docs to Cursor.":"現在，在聊天視窗中，您可以輸入「`@daisyui`」以向 Cursor 提供 daisyUI 文件。","[popover API and anchor positioning `new`](#method-2-popover-api-and-anchor-positioning)":"[popover API 與錨點定位「新」](#method-2-popover-api-and-anchor-positioning) (`new`)","CSS Anchor Positioning is a new standard but isn't yet supported in Firefox and Safari ([caniuse.com](https://caniuse.com/css-anchor-positioning)).":`CSS 錨點定位是一項新標準，但 Firefox 和 Safari 尚不支援 ([caniuse.com](https://caniuse.com/css-anchor-positioning))。`,"In those browsers, the dropdown will appear centered like a modal.":`在這些瀏覽器中，Dropdown 將會像 Modal 一樣居中顯示。`,"There's also [this polyfill](https://github.com/oddbird/css-anchor-positioning) that can be helpful.":`還有[這個polyfill](https://github.com/oddbird/css-anchor-positioning)也很有幫助。`,"[Pikaday](https://github.com/Pikaday/Pikaday) - Works everywhere":`[Pikaday](https://github.com/Pikaday/Pikaday) - 隨處可用`,"Pikaday is a JS datepicker library and you can use it from CDN or as a JS dependency [Read the docs](https://github.com/Pikaday/Pikaday)":`Pikaday 是一個 JS 日期選擇器庫，您可以從 CDN 使用它或作為 JS 依賴項 [閱讀文件](https://github.com/Pikaday/Pikaday)`,"you need to change the span text and the `--value` CSS variable using JS. Value must be a number between 0 and 99.":"您需要使用 JS 更改跨度文字和`--value`CSS variable。數值必須是 0 到 99 之間的數字。","Accordion uses the same style as the [collapse component](/components/collapse/) but it works with radio inputs. You can control which item to be open by checking/unchecking the hidden radio input.":`Accordion 使用與 [Collapse Component](/components/collapse/) 相同的樣式，但它適用於 Radio 輸入。您可以透過選取/取消選取隱藏的 Radio 輸入來控制要開啟的項目。`,"It needs JS to open but it has better accessibility and we can close it using `Esc` key":"它需要 JS 才能打開，但它具有更好的可訪問性，我們可以使用`Esc`鍵關閉它","[Using checkbox](#method-2-checkbox)":`[使用複選框](#method-2-checkbox)`,"`EMAIL`: Your email address":"`EMAIL`：您的電子郵件地址","`FIGMA`: Your Figma API key (optional)":"`FIGMA`：您的 Figma API 金鑰（可選）","`LICENSE`: Your Blueprint license key":"`LICENSE`：您的藍圖許可證金鑰","← Go back to daisyui.com":`← 返回 daisyui.com`,'<a href="/blueprint/">Blueprint</a>: The Official MCP server from daisyUI (Recommended for best results)':`<a href="/blueprint/">Blueprint</a>：來自 daisyUI 的官方 MCP 伺服器（建議以獲得最佳結果）`,'<a href="/docs/mcp/">MCP guides →</a>':`<a href="/docs/mcp/">MCP 指南 →</a>`,'<a href="/docs/skill/">Skill guides →</a>':`<a href="/docs/skill/">技能指南 →</a>`,'<a href="#method-1-details-and-summary">details and summary elements</a>':`<a href="#method-1-details-and-summary">詳細資訊和摘要元素</a>`,'<a href="#method-2-popover-api-and-anchor-positioning-new">popover API and anchor positioning <code>new</code></a>':`<a href="#method-2-popover-api-and-anchor-positioning-new">彈出視窗 API 和錨點定位<code>new</code></a>`,'<a href="#method-3-css-focus">CSS focus</a>':`<a href="#method-3-css-focus">CSS 焦點</a>`,'<a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a>: Free 3rd party MCP server':`<a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a>：免費的第 3 方 MCP 伺服器`,'<a href="https://daisyui.com" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Visit daisyUI</a>':`<a href="https://daisyui.com" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">訪問 daisyUI</a>`,'<a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#enable-a-built-in-theme" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Add the themes you want</a>':`<a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#enable-a-built-in-theme" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">加入你想要的主題</a>`,'<a href="https://daisyui.com/llms.txt" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyui.com/llms.txt</a> file is a compact, text version of daisyUI docs to help AI generate accurate daisyUI code based on your prompt.':`<a href="https://daisyui.com/llms.txt" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyui.com/llms.txt</a> 檔案是 daisyUI 文件的緊湊文字版本，可協助 AI 根據您的提示產生準確的 daisyUI 程式碼。`,'<a href="https://daisyui.com/SKILL.md" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI skill</a> is a compact, markdown version of daisyUI docs to help AI generate accurate daisyUI code based on your prompt.':`<a href="https://daisyui.com/SKILL.md" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI Skill</a> 是 daisyUI 文件的緊湊 Markdown 版本，可協助 AI 根據您的提示產生準確的 daisyUI 程式碼。`,'<a href="https://github.com/gpbl/react-day-picker" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">React Day picker</a> - React only':`<a href="https://github.com/gpbl/react-day-picker" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">React Day 選擇器</a> - 僅 React`,'<a href="https://github.com/uvarov-frontend/vanilla-calendar-pro" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Vanilla Calendar Pro</a> - Works everywhere':`<a href="https://github.com/uvarov-frontend/vanilla-calendar-pro" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Vanilla Calendar Pro</a> - 隨處可用`,'<a href="https://github.com/WickyNilliams/cally" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Cally web component</a> - Works everywhere':`<a href="https://github.com/WickyNilliams/cally" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Cally web Component</a> - 隨處可用`,'<a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a>: Free 3rd party MCP server':`<a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a>：免費的第 3 方 MCP 伺服器`,'<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/flex-basis" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Layout</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/width" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Sizing</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/flex" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Flexbox</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/grid-template-columns" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Grid</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/justify-content" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Box alignment</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/padding" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Spacing</a>':`<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/flex-basis" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Layout</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/width" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Sizing</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/flex" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Flexbox</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/grid-template-columns" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Grid</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/justify-content" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Box alignment</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/padding" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Spacing</a>`,'<a href="svelte:head">svelte:head</a>':`<a href="svelte:head">svelte:head</a>`,"✅ Correct usage:":`✅ 正確用法：`,"✅ Correct: `daisyUI`":"✅ 正確：`daisyUI`","❌ Incorrect usage:":`❌ 錯誤用法：`,"❌ Incorrect: `DaisyUI`, `Daisy UI`, `daisy ui`, `DaisyUi`":"❌ 錯誤：`DaisyUI`、`Daisy UI`、`daisy ui`、`DaisyUi`",'Accordion uses the same style as the <a href="/components/collapse/">collapse component</a> but it works with radio inputs or details elements. You can control which item to be open by checking/unchecking the hidden radio input or setting the open attribute on details element.':`Accordion 使用與 <a href="/components/collapse/">Collapse Component</a> 相同的樣式，但它適用於 Radio 輸入或詳細資料元素。您可以透過選取/取消選取隱藏的 Radio 輸入或在詳細資料元素上設定開啟屬性來控制要開啟的項目。`,"Add this configuration and set your `LICENSE`, `EMAIL`, and optional `FIGMA` variables.":"新增此配置並設定`LICENSE`、`EMAIL`和可選的`FIGMA`變數。","Add this configuration and set your licensing environment variables.":`新增此配置並設定您的許可環境變數。`,"Add this configuration block and set your license details.":`新增此配置區塊並設定您的許可證詳細資訊。`,"Add this configuration to `cline_mcp_settings.json`.":"將此配置新增至`cline_mcp_settings.json`。","Add this configuration to `mcp_config.json`.":"將此配置新增至`mcp_config.json`。","Add this to `claude_desktop_config.json`.":"將其新增至「`claude_desktop_config.json`」。","After configuring the server, tell the AI model to":`配置伺服器後，告訴AI模型`,'Also see <a href="/components/accordion/">accordion</a> examples':`另請參閱<a href="/components/accordion/">手風琴</a>範例`,'As long as you use <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/colors/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI colors</a> they will work on all themes, light or dark.':`只要您使用 <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/colors/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI 顏色</a>，它們就適用於所有主題，無論是淺色還是深色。`,'Blueprint is the official MCP server for daisyUI. <a href="/blueprint/">Read more about Blueprint</a>.':`Blueprint 是 daisyUI 的官方 MCP 伺服器。 <a href="/blueprint/">了解更多關於藍圖的資訊</a>。`,"Brand agreement":`品牌協議`,'Cally is a web component calendar and it works everywhere. <a href="https://github.com/WickyNilliams/cally" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Read the docs</a>':`Cally 是一個網路 Component Calendar，它可以在任何地方使用。 <a href="https://github.com/WickyNilliams/cally" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">閱讀文件</a>`,"Choose `agent: add context server`.":"選擇“agent：新增上下文伺服器”。 (`agent: add context server`)","Click the button below to automatically install in Cursor.":`點擊下方的Button即可自動安裝到Cursor中。`,"Color Picker for daisyUI":`daisyUI 的顏色選擇器`,"Copy/Paste as > Copy link to selection":`複製/貼上為 > 將 Link 複製到選擇`,"Create or edit `opencode.json` in your project root and add the Blueprint MCP configuration.":"在專案根目錄中建立或編輯「`opencode.json`」並新增 Blueprint MCP 配置。","Customer Support":`客戶支援`,"daisyUI Color Picker":`daisyUI 顏色選擇器`,"daisyUI Laravel":`daisyUI Laravel`,"daisyUI Name":`daisyUI 名稱`,'daisyUI name must be written as "daisyUI" with a lowercase "d" and uppercase "UI" with no spaces.':`daisyUI 名稱必須寫為“daisyUI”，其中包含小寫“d”和大寫“UI”，且不帶空格。`,"daisyUI Pro Components":`daisyUI Pro Components`,"daisyUI Store":`daisyUI商店`,'daisyUI supports the <a href="https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-typography" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">TailwindCSS Typography plugin</a>':`daisyUI 支援 <a href="https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-typography" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">TailwindCSS Typography 外掛程式</a>`,"Do not use the daisyUI name or logo in a way that suggests your product or service is officially affiliated with, endorsed by, or produced by daisyUI.":`使用 daisyUI 名稱或標誌時不得暗示您的產品或服務正式隸屬於 daisyUI、由 daisyUI 認可或由 daisyUI 生產。`,'Enable a theme using <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#enable-a-built-in-theme" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><code>data-theme</code></a> on your `<html>` tag:':'在 `<html>` 標籤上使用 <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#enable-a-built-in-theme" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><code>data-theme</code></a> 啟用主題：',"environment variable for the Blueprint MCP server.":`Blueprint MCP 伺服器的環境變數。`,'Every part of daisyUI is <a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@5/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">available on CDN</a> as separate CSS files.':`daisyUI 的每個部分都作為單獨的 CSS 檔案<a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@5/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">在 CDN 上提供</a>。`,"Exception: daisyUI package stays lower case `daisyui` as it is a package name and must follow coding conventions.":"例外：daisyUI 套件保持小寫`daisyui`，因為它是套件名稱，並且必須遵循編碼約定。","file_content:read":`文件內容：已讀`,"file_dev_resources:read":`file_dev_resources：讀取`,"file_metadata:read":`檔案元資料：讀取`,'For a more efficient daisyUI generation and on-demand component snippets, use <a href="/blueprint/">daisyUI Blueprint MCP server</a>. Blueprint MCP saves more tokens and has more control over the generated code.':`若要更有效率地產生 daisyUI 和按需 Component 程式碼段，請使用 <a href="/blueprint/">daisyUI 藍圖 MCP 伺服器</a>。 Blueprint MCP 節省了更多令牌，並且對產生的程式碼有更多控制權。`,'For pagination, we use <a href="/components/join/">join component</a> to show multiple links or buttons next to each other.':`對於 Pagination，我們使用 <a href="/components/join/">join Component</a> 來顯示多個彼此相鄰的連結或按鈕。`,'Get a <a href="/blueprint/checkout/">Blueprint license key</a>.':`取得<a href="/blueprint/checkout/">藍圖許可證金鑰</a>。`,'Get a <a href="/blueprint/checkout/">Blueprint License</a>':`取得<a href="/blueprint/checkout/">藍圖許可證</a>`,'Here\'s a React example to save checkbox state in local storage: <a href="https://stackblitz.com/edit/react-checkbox-localstorage?file=src%2FApp.js" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Stackblitz</a>':`以下是一個在本機儲存中儲存複選框狀態的 React 範例： <a href="https://stackblitz.com/edit/react-checkbox-localstorage?file=src%2FApp.js" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Stackblitz</a>`,'If you already use <a href="/blueprint/">daisyUI Blueprint MCP server</a>, you don\'t need to install this plugin.':`如果您已經使用<a href="/blueprint/">daisyUI Blueprint MCP伺服器</a>，則無需安裝此外掛程式。`,'If you don\'t want to use this feature, <a href="/docs/config/#exclude">you can exclude <code>rootscrollgutter</code></a>.':`如果您不想使用此功能，<a href="/docs/config/#exclude">您可以排除<code>rootscrollgutter</code></a>。`,'If you really need `@tailwindcss/forms` alongside with daisyUI (which I doubt, because both are doing the same job) consider using its <a href="https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-forms#using-only-global-styles-or-only-classes" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><code>strategy: \'class\'</code> config</a> so it only applies style to the elements with specific class name (not all form elements)':`如果你確實需要將 \`@tailwindcss/forms\` 與 daisyUI 一起使用（我對此存疑，因為兩者做的是同一件事），請考慮使用它的 <a href="https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-forms#using-only-global-styles-or-only-classes" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><code>strategy: 'class'</code> config</a>，讓 style 只套用到具有特定 Class name 的 elements（不是所有 form elements）`,'If you really want to use Tailwind\'s `dark:` variant, <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#how-to-apply-tailwinds-dark-selector-for-specific-themes" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">here\'s how to do it</a>.':'如果您確實想使用 Tailwind 的 `dark:` 變體，<a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#how-to-apply-tailwinds-dark-selector-for-specific-themes" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">以下是操作方法</a>。','If you want the collapsed content to be searcheable in browser use the <a href="#-collapse-using-details-and-summary-tag">Collapse using details and summary tag</a>':`如果您希望在瀏覽器中搜尋折疊內容，請使用<a href="#-collapse-using-details-and-summary-tag">使用詳細資訊和摘要標籤折疊</a>`,'If you want the collapsed content to be searcheable in browser use the <a href="#accordion-using-details">Accordion using details</a>':`如果您希望在瀏覽器中可以搜尋折疊的內容，請使用<a href="#accordion-using-details">手風琴使用詳細資訊</a>`,'If you\'re using <a href="/docs/config/#prefix">daisyUI prefix</a>, it will add prefix to `theme-controller` class.':'如果您使用 <a href="/docs/config/#prefix">daisyUI 前綴</a>，它將向 `theme-controller` 類別添加前綴。','If you\'re using <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/styling-with-utility-classes#using-the-prefix-option" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Tailwind CSS prefix</a>, it won\'t add prefix to `theme-controller` class.':'如果您使用 <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/styling-with-utility-classes#using-the-prefix-option" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Tailwind CSS 前綴</a>，它不會為 `theme-controller` 類別加上前綴。','If you\'re using a custom theme make sure you\'re using <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#how-to-add-a-new-custom-theme" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">all the required CSS variables</a>':`如果您使用自訂主題，請確保使用<a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#how-to-add-a-new-custom-theme" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">所有必要的 CSS 變數</a>`,"in Claude Desktop.":`in Claude Desktop.`,"In Cursor press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P, or Ctrl + Shift + P, search for `MCP: Open MCP Settings`, and add this configuration to `mcp.json`:":"在 Cursor 中按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P，或 Ctrl + Shift + P，搜尋“MCP：開啟 MCP 設定”，並將此配置新增至`MCP: Open MCP Settings`： (`mcp.json`)","In Figma, go to":`在 Figma 中，前往`,"In Figma, right click on a section and choose":`在 Figma 中，右鍵單擊一個部分並選擇`,"In your editor, paste the link and ask the LLM to generate daisyUI code for that design.":`在編輯器中，貼上 Link 並要求 LLM 為該設計產生 daisyUI 程式碼。`,'Inputs can be used with `validator` class to have validation styles. <a href="/components/validator/">See Validator component</a> for more details.':'輸入可以與`validator`類別一起使用以具有驗證樣式。 <a href="/components/validator/">請參閱驗證器元件</a>以了解更多詳細資訊。',"Install Codex CLI if you haven't already.":`如果尚未安裝 Codex CLI，請安裝。`,'Install Elixir according to the <a href="https://elixir-lang.org/install.html" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">official Elixir documentation</a>':`根據<a href="https://elixir-lang.org/install.html" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Elixir 官方文件</a>安裝 Elixir`,"Install OpenCode CLI if you haven't already.":`如果尚未安裝 OpenCode CLI，請安裝。`,"library_assets:read":`圖書館資產：已讀`,"library_content:read":`圖書館內容：已讀`,'Make sure you\'re not using <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files#dynamic-class-names" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">dynamic class names</a> (half-variable like `btn-{$color}`). If you do this, there is no way for Tailwind CSS to find your class names.':'請確定您沒有使用<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files#dynamic-class-names" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">動態類別名稱</a>（半變量，例如`btn-{$color}`）。如果您這樣做，Tailwind CSS 將無法找到您的類別名稱。',"My Orders":`我的訂單`,"My Orders (old panel)":`我的訂單（舊面板）`,"My Project: Built with daisyUI":`我的專案：用daisyUI構建`,"Next: Setup the Figma API":`下一步：設定 Figma API`,"Official daisyUI Extension":`官方 daisyUI 擴展`,"On the MCP settings page, set:":`在MCP設定頁面上，設定：`,"Open the Antigravity MCP config file at `~/.gemini/config/mcp_config.json`.":"Open the Antigravity MCP config file at `~/.gemini/config/mcp_config.json`.",'Opening a drawer adds a <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/scrollbar-gutter" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">scrollbar-gutter</a> to the page to avoid layout shift on operating systems that have a fixed scrollbar.':`打開抽屜會在頁面上加上 <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/scrollbar-gutter" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">scrollbar-gutter</a> ，以避免在具有固定滾動條的作業系統上發生佈局變更。`,'Opening a modal adds a <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/scrollbar-gutter" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">scrollbar-gutter</a> to the page to avoid layout shift on operating systems that have a fixed scrollbar.':`開啟 Modal 會在頁面中加入 <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/scrollbar-gutter" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">scrollbar-gutter</a> ，以避免在具有固定滾動條的作業系統上發生變化。`,"Option 1: Automatic setup":`選項 1：自動設定`,"Option 2: Manual setup":`選項 2：手動設定`,"Please do not modify, distort, or alter the logo.":`請勿修改、扭曲或更改徽標。`,"Privacy Policy":`隱私權政策`,'React Day Picker is a flexible date picker component for React. <a href="https://github.com/gpbl/react-day-picker" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Read the docs</a>':`React Day Picker 是 React 的彈性日期選擇器 Component。 <a href="https://github.com/gpbl/react-day-picker" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">閱讀文件</a>`,'Read <a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/copilot/customization/mcp-servers" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">VS Code docs</a> for more info about using MCP.':`有關使用 MCP 的詳細信息，請閱讀 <a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/copilot/customization/mcp-servers" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">VS Code 文件</a>。`,'Read <a href="https://docs.claude.com/en/docs/claude-code/mcp" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Claude Code docs</a> for more info about using MCP.':`Read <a href="https://docs.claude.com/en/docs/claude-code/mcp" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Claude Code docs</a> for more info about using MCP.`,"Required permissions:":`所需權限：`,"Run this command to add the Blueprint MCP server.":`執行此命令以新增 Blueprint MCP 伺服器。`,"Run this command to add the Blueprint MCP server. Figma API Key is optional and only needed for Figma-to-code conversion.":`執行此命令以新增 Blueprint MCP 伺服器。 Figma API 金鑰是可選的，僅在 Figma 轉換到程式碼時需要。`,'Safari has a <a href="https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22261" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">CSS bug</a> since 2008 that prevents button elements from being focused, so we use div `tabindex="0"` as a workaround.':'Safari 自 2008 年起就有一個 <a href="https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22261" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">CSS bug</a>，會阻止 button elements 取得 focus，因此我們使用 div `tabindex="0"` 作為 workaround。',"Search for `MCP: Open User Configuration`.":"搜尋“MCP：開放用戶配置”。 (`MCP: Open User Configuration`)","Search for `Windsurf: MCP Configuration Panel`.":"搜尋“Windsurf：MCP 配置面板”。 (`Windsurf: MCP Configuration Panel`)","Set the Figma API token in the":`在中設定 Figma API 令牌`,"Settings > Security > Personal Access Tokens > Generate new token":`設定 > 安全性 > 個人存取令牌 > 產生新令牌`,'So you can use `bg-primary`, `border-secondary`, etc. Read more about <a href="/docs/utilities/">daisyUI color utility classes</a>.':'因此，您可以使用 `bg-primary`、`border-secondary` 等。了解有關 <a href="/docs/utilities/">daisyUI 顏色實用程式類別</a>的更多資訊。','Some uncommon Tailwind CSS color utility classes for daisyUI colors are available on additional CSS files for CDN usage, see <a href="/docs/colors/#how-to-use">colors docs</a> for more info.':`一些不常見的用於 daisyUI 顏色的 Tailwind CSS 顏色實用程式類別可在用於 CDN 使用的其他 CSS 檔案上使用，請參閱<a href="/docs/colors/#how-to-use">顏色文件</a>以了解更多資訊。`,"Step 1: Get a Figma Access Token":`第 1 步：取得 Figma 訪問令牌`,"Step 1: License key":`第 1 步：許可證密鑰`,"Step 2: Add the token to Blueprint MCP":`步驟 2：將令牌新增至 Blueprint MCP`,"Step 2: Configure MCP settings":`步驟 2：設定 MCP 設定`,"Step 2: Install Codex CLI":`第 2 步：安裝 Codex CLI`,"Step 2: Install OpenCode CLI":`第 2 步：安裝 OpenCode CLI`,"Step 3: Configure MCP settings":`步驟 3：設定 MCP 設定`,"Step 3: Copy a Figma selection link":`步驟 3：複製 Figma 選擇 Link`,"Step 4: Ask your editor to generate daisyUI code":`第 4 步：請編輯器產生 daisyUI 程式碼`,"team_library_content:read":`team_library_content：已讀`,"Terms and Conditions":`條款與條件`,"Theme Generator made with daisyUI":`使用 daisyUI 製作的主題產生器`,'To setup Tailwind CSS syntax support and IntelliSense, see <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/editor-setup" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Tailwind CSS docs</a>.':`要設定 Tailwind CSS syntax 支援和 IntelliSense，請參閱 <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/editor-setup" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Tailwind CSS 文件</a>。`,'Try using `@source` <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files#explicitly-registering-sources" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Explicitly register sources</a>':'嘗試使用 `@source` <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files#explicitly-registering-sources" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">明確註冊來源</a>',"Unofficial daisyUI datepicker":`非官方 daisyUI 日期選擇器`,'Using Tailwind CSS and daisyUI, it is expected for CSS files to be very small. Ideally only the class names you used must be in the CSS file. Sometimes (specially in monorepos) it is possible that <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Tailwind CSS automatic class name detection</a> finds some unwanted strings in your project and generate styles for them. To avoid this, you can <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files#disabling-automatic-detection" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">disable automatic detection</a> and register your source files using `@source` directive.':'使用 Tailwind CSS 和 daisyUI 時，CSS 檔案預期會很小。理想情況下，CSS 檔案中只應包含你使用過的 Class name。有時（特別是在 monorepos 中），<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Tailwind CSS automatic class name detection</a> 可能會在專案中找到不需要的字串並為它們產生 styles。為避免這種情況，你可以 <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files#disabling-automatic-detection" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">disable automatic detection</a>，並使用 `@source` directive 註冊 source files。','Vanilla Calendar Pro is a JavaScript calendar library. <a href="https://github.com/uvarov-frontend/vanilla-calendar-pro" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Read the docs</a>':`Vanilla Calendar Pro 是一個 JavaScript 日曆函式庫。 <a href="https://github.com/uvarov-frontend/vanilla-calendar-pro" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">閱讀文件</a>`,'We recommend using an <a href="/docs/mcp/">MCP server</a> for daisyUI.':`我們建議為 daisyUI 使用 <a href="/docs/mcp/">MCP 伺服器</a>。`,'When naming your projects, tools, or services, use "for daisyUI" or "compatible with daisyUI" instead of including "daisyUI" at the beginning of your product name.':`命名您的專案、工具或服務時，請使用“for daisyUI”或“與 daisyUI 相容”，而不是在產品名稱的開頭包含“daisyUI”。`,'With daisyUI, you don\'t need to manually set colors using <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/colors/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><code>dark:</code> variant</a>':`使用 daisyUI，您無需使用 <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/colors/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><code>dark:</code> 變體</a> 手動設定顏色`,'You can also use the native HTML `<input type="date">` for a date picker. <a href="/components/input/#date-input">Read more</a>':'您也可以使用原生 HTML `<input type="date">` 作為日期選擇器。 <a href="/components/input/#date-input">了解更多</a>','You can create a dedicated `Workspace` where you can upload the `llms.txt` file. To download the file, visit <a href="https://daisyui.com/llms.txt" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">https://daisyui.com/llms.txt</a>, right-click, and select "Save As...". Once downloaded, upload the file as an attachment in the Grok Workspace.':'您可以建立一個專用的“工作區”，您可以在其中上傳`Workspace`檔案。若要下載文件，請造訪 <a href="https://daisyui.com/llms.txt" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">https://daisyui.com/llms.txt</a>，右鍵單擊，然後 Select「另存為...」。下載後，將文件作為附件上傳到 Grok 工作區。 (`llms.txt`)',"You can download the daisyUI logo in SVG and PNG formats for appropriate usage.":`您可以下載 SVG 和 PNG 格式的 daisyUI 標誌以供適當使用。`,'You can setup daisyUI\'s llms.txt file to your workspace so Copilot can use it by default. (<a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/copilot/customization/overview" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Read more at VSCode docs</a>)':`您可以將 daisyUI 的 llms.txt 檔案設定到您的工作區，以便 Copilot 可以透過 Default 使用它。 （<a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/copilot/customization/overview" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">在 VSCode 文件中了解更多</a>）`,'You can setup daisyUI\'s llms.txt file to your workspace so Cursor can use it by default. (<a href="https://docs.cursor.com/context/rules" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Read more at Cursor docs</a>)':`您可以將 daisyUI 的 llms.txt 檔案設定到您的工作區，以便 Cursor 可以透過 Default 使用它。 （<a href="https://docs.cursor.com/context/rules" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">在 Cursor 文件中了解更多</a>）`,'You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Claude Code.':`You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Claude Code.`,'You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Claude desktop.':`You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Claude desktop.`,'You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Cline.':`你可以在 Cline 中使用 <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> 或 <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> 作為 MCP server。`,'You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Cursor.':`你可以在 Cursor 中使用 <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> 或 <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> 作為 MCP server。`,'You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in VSCode.':`您可以使用 <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> 或 <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> 作為 VSCode 中的 MCP ode 中的 MCPode 伺服器。`,'You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Windsurf.':`你可以在 Windsurf 中使用 <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> 或 <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> 作為 MCP server。`,'You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Zed.':`你可以在 Zed 中使用 <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> 或 <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> 作為 MCP server。`,"Discount code":`折扣碼`,"Limited time discount code":`限時優惠碼`,"code at checkout to get":`結帳時取得代碼`,"discount.":`折扣。`,"Remaining time":`剩餘時間`,Convert:i,"Install guide":`安裝指南`,"Get the license":`獲得許可證`,"Figma API to LLM":`Figma API 轉 LLM`,"I will do my best to help you.":`我會盡力幫助你。`,"What happens after I pay?":`我付款後會發生什麼事？`,"Will I receive updates?":`我會收到更新嗎？`,"Do I get customer support?":`我可以獲得客戶支援嗎？`,"Can I cancel my subscription?":`我可以取消訂閱嗎？`,"Can I get a refund?":`我可以退款嗎？`,"I didn't receive the email":`我沒有收到電子郵件`,"I bought the wrong package":`我買錯了包包`,"There was an issue with the payment":`付款出現問題`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Antigravity":`Install Blueprint MCP for Antigravity`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Antigravity.":`Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Antigravity.`,"After configuring the server, tell the AI model to use Blueprint MCP.":`配置伺服器後，告訴 AI 模型使用 Blueprint MCP。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Claude Desktop":`Install Blueprint MCP for Claude Desktop`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Claude Desktop.":`Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Claude Desktop.`,"Go to Settings > Developer in Claude Desktop.":`Go to Settings > Developer in Claude Desktop.`,"Click the Edit Config button.":`點選編輯配置 Button。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Claude Code":`Install Blueprint MCP for Claude Code`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Claude Code.":`Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Claude Code.`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Cline":`安裝 Cline 藍圖 MCP`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Cline.":`為 Cline 安裝 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 伺服器。`,"Select the Configure tab.":`Select 配置選項卡。`,"Click the Configure MCP Servers button at the bottom of the pane.":`按一下窗格底部的設定 MCP 伺服器 Button。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Codex":`安裝 Codex 藍圖 MCP`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Codex.":`安裝 Codex 的 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 伺服器。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Cursor":`為 Cursor 安裝藍圖 MCP`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Cursor.":`為 Cursor 安裝 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 伺服器。`,"Setup Figma API for Blueprint MCP":`為 Blueprint MCP 設定 Figma API`,"Generate daisyUI code from a Figma design file":`從 Figma 設計檔案產生 daisyUI 程式碼`,"In Figma, go to Settings > Security > Personal Access Tokens > Generate new token.":`在 Figma 中，前往設定 > 安全性 > 個人存取權令牌 > 產生新令牌。`,"Set the Figma API token in the FIGMA environment variable for the Blueprint MCP server.":`在 Blueprint MCP 伺服器的 FigMA 環境變數中設定 Figma API 令牌。`,"In Figma, right click on a section and choose Copy/Paste as > Copy link to selection.":`在 Figma 中，右鍵點選某個部分並選擇複製/貼上為 > 將 Link 複製到所選內容。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for OpenClaw":`安裝 OpenClaw 的 Blueprint MCP`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for OpenClaw.":`為 OpenClaw 安裝 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 伺服器。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for OpenCode":`安裝 Blueprint MCP for OpenCode`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for OpenCode.":`安裝適用於 OpenCode 的 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 伺服器。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for VSCode Copilot":`安裝適用於 VSCode Copilot 的 Blueprint MCP`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for VSCode Copilot.":`為 VSCode Copilot 安裝 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 伺服器。`,"In VS Code press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P, or Ctrl + Shift + P.":`在 VS Code 中，按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P 或 Ctrl + Shift + P。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Windsurf":`為 Windsurf 安裝藍圖 MCP`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Windsurf.":`為 Windsurf 安裝 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 伺服器。`,"Press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P, or Ctrl + Shift + P.":`按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P 或 Ctrl + Shift + P。`,"Click Add custom server +.":`按一下新增自訂伺服器 +。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Zed":`安裝適用於 Zed 的 Blueprint MCP`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Zed.":`為 Zed 安裝 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 伺服器。`,"In Zed press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P, or Ctrl + Shift + P.":`在 Zed 中按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P 或 Ctrl + Shift + P。`,"Branding and logo usage guidelines for daisyUI":`daisyUI 的品牌和標誌使用指南`,'To close the dropdown after click, you can use something like `onclick="document.activeElement.blur()"`. <a href="https://play.tailwindcss.com/pc8zXb89lM" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Example</a>':'若要在點擊後關閉 Dropdown，您可以使用類似 `onclick="document.activeElement.blur()"` 的方法。 <a href="https://play.tailwindcss.com/pc8zXb89lM" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">範例</a>',"Press F to pay respects.":`按F表示敬意。`,"Press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P. Or if it's Windows, press ⌃ Ctrl + ⇧ Shift + P.":`按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P。或如果是 Windows，請按 ⌃ Ctrl + ⇧ Shift + P。`,"In Cursor press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P ( Or Ctrl + Shift + P )":`在 Cursor 中按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P （或 Ctrl + Shift + P ）`,"In VS Code press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P ( Or Ctrl + Shift + P )":`在 VS Code 中按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P （或 Ctrl + Shift + P ）`,"Press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P (or ⌃ Ctrl + ⇧ Shift + P on Windows)":`按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P（或在 Windows 上按 ⌃ Ctrl + ⇧ Shift + P）`,"In Zed press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P ( Or Ctrl + Shift + P )":`在 Zed 中按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P （或 Ctrl + Shift + P ）`,"Open Cursor settings with ⌘ + ,":`使用 ⌘ + 開啟 Cursor 設置，`,"daisyUI community articles":`daisyUI 社群文章`,"Tailwind CSS articles and daisyUI tutorials":`Tailwind CSS 文章和 daisyUI 教學課程`,"daisyUI community courses":`daisyUI 社群課程`,"Free Tailwind CSS courses and best Tailwind CSS tutorials":`免費 Tailwind CSS 課程和最佳 Tailwind CSS 教程`,"daisyUI community videos":`daisyUI 社群視頻`,"Best Tailwind CSS video tutorials and Free Tailwind CSS video courses":`最佳 Tailwind CSS 影片教學與免費 Tailwind CSS 影片課程`,"Official daisyUI Skills":`官方daisyUI技能`,"Enough with AI slop":`受夠了 AI slop`,"Setup your coding agent to generate better UI.":`設定 coding agent 以產生更好的 UI。`,"Compatible with all coding agents":`與所有coding agents相容`,"Coming soon…":`即將推出…`,"daisyUI Skills":`daisyUI技能`,"daisyUI Skills - Tailwind CSS Skill":`daisyUI Skills - Tailwind CSS Skill`,"daisyUI and Tailwind CSS theme generator":`daisyUI 與 Tailwind CSS 主題產生器`,"Tailwind CSS Theme Generator for daisyUI - Custom Tailwind CSS themes with light mode and dark mode support":`Tailwind CSS Theme Generator for daisyUI - 自訂 Tailwind CSS 主題，支援淺色模式和深色模式`,"Sales volume reached $12,450 this week, showing a 15% increase from the previous period.":`本週銷量達 12,450 美元，較上期成長 15%。`,Size:a,"Click the MCP Servers icon at the top navigation bar of the Cline pane.":`Click the MCP Servers icon at the top navigation bar of the Cline pane.`,"Select the  tab.":`Select the  tab.`,"Click the  button at the bottom of the pane.":`Click the  button at the bottom of the pane.`,"After configuring the server, tell the AI model to .":`After configuring the server, tell the AI model to .`,"Go to  in Claude Desktop.":`Go to  in Claude Desktop.`,"Click the  button.":`Click the  button.`,"Click .":`Click .`,"install-btn":`install-btn`,"MCP server":`MCP server`,day:`day`,hour:s,min:`min`,sec:`sec`,Use:`Use`,copied:d,copy:f,close:p,and:`and`,"to daisyUI":`to daisyUI`,"Compatible with":`Compatible with`,"and more":`and more`,"Design System":`Design System`,Resources:h,Solution:g,Providing:_,context:v,It:`It`,Introducing:b,"for daisyUI":`for daisyUI`,variants:x,variables:S,"to generate daisyUI code":`to generate daisyUI code`,"Generate daisyUI code":`Generate daisyUI code`,"daisyUI Blueprint MCP server":`daisyUI Blueprint MCP server`,Examples:C,"Blueprint free trial":`Blueprint 免費試用`,"3-day free trial":`3 天免費試用`,", cancel anytime.":`，可隨時取消。`,"Get Your Blueprint License":`獲取你的 Blueprint License`,"This page was made with Blueprint MCP":`此頁面由 Blueprint MCP`,"The Official":`The Official`,"UI Generator":`UI Generator`,"Creative Director":`Creative Director`,"Page Architect":`Page Architect`,"Design System Expert":`Design System Expert`,"MCP Server":`MCP 伺服器`,"The most powerful agentic UI workflow in an MCP server":`MCP 服務器中最強大的 agentic UI workflow`,"10× better code quality":`代碼質量提升 10 倍`,"10× faster results":`結果快 10 倍`,"90% lower token costs":`token 成本降低 90%`,"Provides on-demand, fine-tuned UI design knowledge to your AI agent":`為你的 AI 代理按需提供精調的 UI 設計知識`,"After purchase, your license key arrives by email.":`購買後，license 密鑰会通過電子郵件發送給你。`,"Install the MCP server, add the key, and ask your agent to use Blueprint.":`安裝 MCP 服務器，添加密鑰，并要求你的代理使用 Blueprint。`,"One-shots generated by daisyUI Blueprint MCP":`由 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 生成的一次成型作品`,"Interface examples":`界面示例`,"Blueprint MCP server works with coding agents":`Blueprint MCP 服務器可與coding agents配合使用`,"ALL WEBSITES LOOK THE SAME":`所有网站看起來都一樣`,"Sick of":`厌倦了`,"AI slop?":`AI slop?`,"AI-generated sites arrive with outdated dependencies, stale syntax, copy-paste layouts, the same color palettes, purple gradients, inconsistent spacing, and a structure so mediocre that no one wants to use it.":`AI 生成的网站往往帶着過時依賴、陈舊語法、複制粘贴式布局、相同的配色、紫色漸變、不一致的間距，以及平庸到没人想用的結構。`,"Example of a generic AI-generated landing page":`通用 AI 生成落地頁示例`,"The most mediocre layout":`最平庸的布局`,"Boring, inauthentic color palette":`无聊且不真實的配色`,"Looks like every other AI-generated site":`看起來像其他所有 AI 生成网站`,"Inconsistent components, no design system":`組件不一致，没有設計系統`,"Inaccessible, inefficient, and unmaintainable code":`不可訪問、低效且難維護的代碼`,"AI slop content and lack of structure":`AI slop 內容和結構缺失`,"Purple gradients everywhere":`到處都是紫色漸變`,"TRYING TO FIX THE SLOP WITH INSTRUCTIONS?":`想用指令修複這些垃圾？`,"Your LLM ignores the instructions and skills.":`你的 LLM 會忽略指令和技能。`,"Agent skills are collections of instructions and rules. Check the logs and the pattern is familiar: the model reads a few files, skips the rest, ignores inconvenient rules, and moves on.":`代理技能是一組指令和規則。查看日誌就會看到熟悉的模式：模型讀幾個檔案，跳過其餘檔案，忽略麻煩的規則，然後繼續。`,"UI work needs more context than most tasks. Yet as the instruction set grows, the chance of selective reading grows with it.":`UI 工作比大多數任務需要更多 context。但指令集越大，選擇性閱讀的概率也越高。`,"Skill files inspected":`已檢查的技能檔案`,"Ignored 40% of the rules":`忽略了 40% 的規則`,"Skipped 23 files due to overconfidence":`因過度自信跳過 23 個文件`,"Ignored the rules and treated them as suggestions only":`忽略規則，只把它们当作建議`,read:w,"Lines 1 to 120":`第 1 到 120 行`,"partially ignored":`部分忽略`,skipped:T,"The model continued without following the rules it was expected to follow.":`模型没有遵守應当遵守的規則就繼續了。`,"Wasted time, wasted effort, wasted tokens":`浪費時間，浪費精力，浪費 token`,"Tired of wasting tokens?":`厌倦浪費 token 了吗？`,"Without clear instructions, AI creates the same generic UI for everyone. That's why trends like purple buttons and gradients quickly became overused.":`没有清晰指令時，AI 会為每個人創建同樣的通用 UI。這就是紫色按鈕和漸變等趨勢很快被滥用的原因。`,"Making the design unique takes many prompts, additional edits, wasted time, and LOTS of tokens.":`之後再讓設計變得獨特，就需要大量提示詞、額外修改、浪費時間和大量 token。`,"What if...":`如果……`,"you could one-shot a unique, original, and functional UI without any effort?":`你可以毫不費力地一次生成獨特、原創且可用的 UI？`,"No slop. No skip. No waste.":`无垃圾。无跳過。无浪費。`,"Meet the Blueprint MCP tools":`認識 Blueprint MCP 工具`,"THE REAL SOLUTION":`真正的解决方案`,"Blueprint fixes that.":`Blueprint 修複了這一点。`,"Introducing a mandatory MCP workflow.":`引入強制 MCP workflow。`,"Every tool has a defined job and a strict execution order. Each tool provides the necessary resources and functionality to your agent. The agent must follow these rules sequentially. It cannot skip steps, invent component syntax, or mark unfinished work as complete.":`每個工具都有明確职责和嚴格的執行順序。每個工具都会向你的代理提供必要資源和功能。代理必須按順序遵守這些規則。它不能跳過步驟、編造組件語法，或把未完成的工作標記為完成。`,"Rules and principles":`規則和原則`,"LLM is forced to read and follow":`LLM 被強制閱讀并遵守`,"Page architectures":`頁面架構`,"Matched by intent":`按意圖匹配`,"daisyUI components":`daisyUI 元件`,"Syntax, examples, code snippets":`語法、示例、代碼片段`,"Final inspection":`最终檢查`,"Finds and fixes visual issues":`發現并修複視覺問題`,"Convert everything to daisyUI.":`把所有內容转換為 daisyUI。`,"Blueprint gives your agent the tools to understand the source first. It extracts the structure, chooses the matching daisyUI components, supplies exact snippets, and checks the conversion when the code is done.":`Blueprint 先給你的代理理解源內容的工具。它提取結構，選擇匹配的 daisyUI 組件，提供精確片段，并在代碼完成後檢查转換結果。`,"Figma converts to daisyUI":`Figma 转換為 daisyUI`,"Tailwind CSS converts to daisyUI":`Tailwind CSS 转換為 daisyUI`,"Screenshot converts to daisyUI":`截圖轉換為 daisyUI`,Screenshot:E,"Bootstrap converts to daisyUI":`Bootstrap 转換為 daisyUI`,"Image palette converts to daisyUI":`圖片調色板转換為 daisyUI`,"Image color palette":`圖片調色板`,"Picture color palette to a daisyUI theme":`圖片調色板转換為 daisyUI 主題`,"See Blueprint in action":`觀看 Blueprint 實際运行`,"Watch Blueprint's MCP server create unique, authentic UIs from a simple prompt. The server gives your AI agent the context it needs: design-system principles, code snippets, and UX direction. When the page is finished, Blueprint inspects the code and fixes visual issues.":`觀看 Blueprint 的 MCP 伺服器如何從一個簡單提示詞建立獨特、真實的 UI。伺服器會給你的 AI 代理所需的 context：設計系統原則、程式碼片段和 UX 方向。頁面完成後，Blueprint 會檢查程式碼並修復視覺問題。`,"Blueprint MCP server converts a Figma design to daisyUI":`Blueprint MCP 服務器將 Figma 設計转換為 daisyUI`,"Blueprint MCP server converts Tailwind CSS to daisyUI":`Blueprint MCP 服務器將 Tailwind CSS 转換為 daisyUI`,"COMPARE WITH OTHER OPTIONS":`與其他選項比較`,"All-in-one.":`一体化。`,"Documentation context helps an LLM answer questions. Blueprint surrounds that official source with project setup, creative direction, page architecture, exact component retrieval, conversion workflows, and a final inspection gate.":`文档 context 能帮助 LLM 回答問題。Blueprint 在這份official來源之外加入項目設置、創意方向、頁面架構、精確組件檢索、转換 workflows 和最终檢查关卡。`,"Comparison of daisyUI Blueprint MCP, daisyUI Skill, Context7 MCP, and GitMCP":`daisyUI Blueprint MCP、daisyUI 技能、Context7 MCP 和 GitMCP 對比`,"Need something else? Email":`還需要别的？發送郵件`,"and we will help.":`我们会帮忙。`,"The official daisyUI MCP server":`official daisyUI MCP 服務器`,"Your license key arrives by email.":`你的 license 密鑰会通過電子郵件發送。`,"Add it to the MCP server and ask your coding agent to use Blueprint.":`將它添加到 MCP 服務器，并要求你的編碼代理使用 Blueprint。`,"v1.5":`v1.5`,"July 2026":`2026 年 7 月`,"Blueprint now helps your LLM generate the whole UI, not only individual components.":`Blueprint 現在帮助你的 LLM 生成整個 UI，而不只是單個組件。`,"MCP tools":`MCP 工具`,"New: daisyUI Setup Expert. Knows how to set up and configure daisyUI, themes, fonts, and icons.":`新增：daisyUI 設定專家。了解如何設定和配置 daisyUI、主題、字體和圖示。`,"New: daisyUI Rules Enforcer. Enforces the rules and principles.":`新增：daisyUI Rules Enforcer。強制執行規則和原則。`,"New: daisyUI Creative Director. Provides a design trends catalog, UX principles, creative decisions, and taste.":`新增：daisyUI Creative Director。提供設計趨勢目錄、UX 原則、創意决策和品味。`,"New: daisyUI Page Architect. Knows how to structure pages and layouts, what content they need, and which components to use.":`新增： daisyUI Page Architect.了解如何組織頁面和版面、需要哪些內容以及使用哪些元件。`,"Updated: daisyUI Component Syntax Expert. Provides exact code syntax, daisyUI snippets, and examples.":`更新：daisyUI Component Syntax Expert。提供精確代碼語法、daisyUI 片段和示例。`,"New: daisyUI Quality Inspector. Checks design and code quality, then requires the LLM to fix any issues.":`新增：daisyUI Quality Inspector。檢查設計和代碼質量，然後要求 LLM 修複所有問題。`,"Updated: Figma to daisyUI. Improved Figma conversion.":`更新：Figma to daisyUI。改进 Figma 转換。`,Prompts:D,"The Tailwind CSS, Bootstrap, and Screenshot to daisyUI prompts, plus Image to daisyUI theme, are now available as MCP tools. MCP clients that don't support MCP prompts can use them too.":`Tailwind CSS、Bootstrap、截圖轉 daisyUI 的提示詞，以及圖片轉 daisyUI 主題，現在都可作為 MCP 工具使用。不支援 MCP 提示詞的 MCP 用戶端也能使用它們。`,"MCP resources":`MCP 資源`,"Updated: Snippet":`更新：程式碼片段`,"New: Setup":`新增：設定`,"New: Rule":`新增：規則`,"New: Page":`新增：頁面`,"Setup Expert":`設定專家`,Mandatory:O,"Reads the repo first. It understands dependencies, framework, configuration, themes, colors, fonts, icons, and file structure before your agent changes a pixel.":`先讀取 repo。它会在你的代理修改任何像素前理解依賴、框架、配置、主題、颜色、字体、圖標和文件結構。`,"Your agent gets the daisyUI install instructions, daisyUI config, and daisyUI custom theme setup when needed.":`你的代理会在需要時獲得 daisyUI 安裝说明、daisyUI 配置和 daisyUI 自定義主題設置。`,"Installing daisyUI":`安裝 daisyUI`,"Adding custom theme, fonts and icons":`添加自定義主題、字体和圖標`,"Rules Enforcer":`規則執行器`,"Loads implementation, syntax, accessibility, responsive, theme, media, and quality rules as requirements your LLM must follow.":`將實現、語法、可訪問性、響應式、主題、媒体和質量規則作為你的 LLM 必須遵守的要求加載。`,"The workflow cannot continue by skimming half a skill file and quietly dropping the difficult constraints.":`workflow 不能只快速瀏覽半個技能檔案，然後悄悄丟掉困難約束就繼續。`,"Enforced design rules and code instructions":`已執行設計規則和代碼指令`,"Creative direction":`創意方向`,"Directs UX, content, originality, color, composition, typography, imagery, design trends, and motion as one coherent idea.":`把 UX、內容、原創性、颜色、構圖、排版、圖像、設計趨勢和動效作為一個连貫想法來指導。`,"Instead of another purple-gradient template, the page gets a point of view connected to its product and audience.":`頁面不会再是另一個紫色漸變模板，而是獲得與產品和受眾相关的觀点。`,"Applied creative design rules":`已應用創意設計規則`,"Applied UI/UX principles":`已應用 UI/UX 原則`,"Applied an appropriate design trend":`已應用合适的設計趨勢`,Architecture:k,"Chooses from 211 page architectures covering purpose, structure, content, goals, states, edge cases, and component composition.":`從 211 個頁面架構中選擇，覆盖目的、結構、內容、目標、状態、邊缘情况和組件組合。`,"Your LLM stops guessing what belongs on the page. It gets a production plan shaped around the job the page must do.":`你的 LLM 不再猜頁面该有什么。它会得到围绕頁面任務塑造的生產計划。`,"Accessing page architecture library":`訪問頁面架構庫`,"Finding the best layout structure":`寻找最佳布局結構`,"Component Syntax Expert":`元件語法專家`,"Retrieves exact, correct daisyUI component structures, variants, code snippets, and examples only when the page needs them.":`仅在頁面需要時檢索精確、正確的 daisyUI 組件結構、變体、代碼片段和示例。`,"No stale syntax from model memory. No utility pile pretending to be a maintained component.":`没有來自模型記忆的陈舊語法。没有把 utility 堆当成受維護組件。`,"Received daisyUI components and rules":`已收到 daisyUI 組件和規則`,"Received code snippets and examples":`已收到代碼片段和示例`,"Quality Inspector":`品質檢查員`,"Final gate":`最終關卡`,"Audits the finished source for visual problems, syntax errors, accessibility issues, responsive failures, and ignored rules.":`審查完成後的源代碼，查找視覺問題、語法錯誤、可訪問性問題、響應式失败和被忽略的規則。`,"When the inspection finds a problem, your agent has to fix it before the workflow can call the page finished.":`当檢查發現問題時，你的代理必須修複它，workflow 才能称頁面完成。`,"Fixed syntax issues":`已修複語法問題`,"Fixed visual design problems":`已修複視覺設計問題`,"Front-end skill":`前端技能`,"Make an admin dashboard for server management with Retro-Futurism style":`用 Retro-Futurism 風格制作一個服務器管理後台`,"UI skills":`UI 技能`,"Make an email client UI with clean design":`制作一個干净設計的郵件客戶端 UI`,"daisyUI skill":`daisyUI 技能`,"Make a dense Japanese news website with Maximalism style":`用 Maximalism 風格制作一個密集的日本新聞网站`,"UI design agent":`UI 設計代理`,"Make a product management dashboard for managing SaaS businesses":`制作一個用于管理 SaaS 業務的產品管理仪表盘`,"Design website with Codex":`用 Codex 設計網站`,"Make an online shop with Skeuomorphism design for selling gaming headphones":`制作一個用于销售游戏耳機的 Skeuomorphism 風格网店`,"AI site maker":`AI 網站生成器`,"Make a landing page for a cute cafe in Seul":`為首尔一家可爱咖啡馆制作落地頁`,"Tailwind CSS skill":`Tailwind CSS 技能`,"Make an event website for a dev confrence in Tokyo":`為東京的開發者会議制作活動网站`,"Best UI design skill":`最佳 UI 設計技能`,"Make a Swiss design style landingpage for a nordic style furniture manifacturer":`為北欧風家具制造商制作 Swiss design 風格落地頁`,"Front-end agent":`前端代理`,"Make an artistic personal site for a photographer":`為攝影师制作藝術個人网站`,"Figma to daisyUI":`Figma 轉 daisyUI`,"Reads frames, hierarchy, auto layout, type, color, component instances, and a rendered preview before matching daisyUI patterns.":`在匹配 daisyUI 模式前讀取 frame、層級、auto layout、類型、颜色、組件實例和渲染預覽。`,"Tailwind CSS to daisyUI":`Tailwind CSS 轉 daisyUI`,"Preserves layout and behavior while replacing hand-built component utility stacks with current daisyUI structures.":`在用当前 daisyUI 結構替換手写組件 utility 堆的同時，保留布局和行為。`,"Screenshot to daisyUI":`截圖轉 daisyUI`,"Analyzes hierarchy, density, states, and responsive clues, then rebuilds the reference with accessible daisyUI components.":`分析層級、密度、状態和響應式線索，然後用可訪問的 daisyUI 組件重建参考。`,"Bootstrap to daisyUI":`Bootstrap 轉 daisyUI`,"Maps Bootstrap components to daisyUI while keeping the content, semantics, structure, and interaction model intact.":`將 Bootstrap 組件映射到 daisyUI，同時保持內容、語義、結構和交互模型完整。`,"Image to daisyUI theme":`圖片轉 daisyUI 主題`,"Extracts an image palette, assigns semantic roles, calculates readable content colors, and generates every required daisyUI theme variable.":`提取圖片調色板，分配語義角色，計算可讀內容颜色，并生成所有必需的 daisyUI 主題變量。`,"daisyUI <div class='-my-1 inline-grid grid-cols-[.25rem_1fr_.25rem] grid-rows-[.25rem_1fr_.25rem] align-middle'><div class='border-s border-t border-blue-600 [grid-area:1/1/2/2]'></div><div class='border-e border-t border-blue-600 [grid-area:1/3/2/4]'></div><div class='border-s border-b border-blue-600 [grid-area:3/1/4/2]'></div><div class='border-e border-b border-blue-600 [grid-area:3/3/4/4]'></div><div class='font-title m-0.5 bg-blue-600 px-1 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-white [grid-area:1/1/4/4]'>BLUEPRINT</div></div> MCP":`daisyUI <div class='-my-1 inline-grid grid-cols-[.25rem_1fr_.25rem] grid-rows-[.25rem_1fr_.25rem] align-middle'><div class='border-s border-t border-blue-600 [grid-area:1/1/2/2]'></div><div class='border-e border-t border-blue-600 [grid-area:1/3/2/4]'></div><div class='border-s border-b border-blue-600 [grid-area:3/1/4/2]'></div><div class='border-e border-b border-blue-600 [grid-area:3/3/4/4]'></div><div class='font-title m-0.5 bg-blue-600 px-1 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-white [grid-area:1/1/4/4]'>BLUEPRINT</div></div> MCP`,"daisyUI Skill":`daisyUI 技能`,"Context7 MCP":`Context7 MCP`,GitMCP:A,"daisyUI Official":`daisyUI Official`,"Fine-tuned for daisyUI":`為 daisyUI 精調`,"<span class='text-error'>Impossible to fine-tune</span>":`<span class='text-error'>无法精調</span>`,"Data source":`資料來源`,"<span class='text-success'>Authored & verified</span>":`<span class='text-success'>編写并驗證</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>AI-generated</span>":`<span class='text-error'>AI 生成</span>`,"Resource accuracy":`資源準確性`,"<span class='text-success'>100% accurate</span>":`<span class='text-success'>100% 準確</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>Confuses random repos</span>":`<span class='text-error'>混淆隨機 repos</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>Confuses random pages</span>":`<span class='text-error'>混淆隨機頁面</span>`,"Includes unwanted context":`包含不需要的 context`,"<span class='text-success'>No</span>":`<span class='text-success'>否</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>Depends on the LLM</span>":`<span class='text-error'>取决于 LLM</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>Yes</span>":`<span class='text-error'>是</span>`,"211 page architectures":`211 個頁面架構`,"Design trends catalog":`設計趨勢目錄`,"Code snippets":`程式碼片段`,"Quality inspection":`品質檢查`,"daisyUI design system specs":`daisyUI 設計系統規格`,"Converts Figma to daisyUI":`將 Figma 转換為 daisyUI`,"Converts Tailwind CSS to daisyUI":`將 Tailwind CSS 转換為 daisyUI`,"Converts Bootstrap to daisyUI":`將 Bootstrap 转換為 daisyUI`,"Generates themes from an image":`從圖片生成主題`,"Provides component pictures to AI":`向 AI 提供組件圖片`,"Generates AI slop":`生成 AI slop`,"<span class='text-success'>Less likely</span>":`<span class='text-success'>可能性更低</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>More likely</span>":`<span class='text-error'>可能性更高</span>`,"<span class='text-success'>Synced with daisyUI</span>":`<span class='text-success'>與 daisyUI 同步</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>Depends on a crawler</span>":`<span class='text-error'>取决于爬虫</span>`,"Token usage efficiency":`Token 使用效率`,"<span class='text-success'>Super efficient</span>":`<span class='text-success'>非常高效</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>Not efficient</span>":`<span class='text-error'>不高效</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>Wastes tokens on unrelated context</span>":`<span class='text-error'>在无关 context 上浪費 token</span>`,"Is this a one-time payment or a subscription?":`這是一次性付款還是訂閱？`,"Both are possible. You can purchase a monthly license, yearly license, or lifetime license.":`两種都可以。你可以購買月度 license、年度 license 或终身 license。`,"You will receive an email with a license key that you can use to activate the MCP server. If you don't see the email, check your spam folder.":`你会收到一封包含 license 密鑰的電子郵件，可用于激活 MCP 服務器。如果没有看到郵件，請檢查垃圾郵件文件夹。`,"Yes. Blueprint is updated automatically with the latest version of daisyUI. New MCP tools, resources, and prompts are added automatically.":`是的。Blueprint 会自動更新到最新版本的 daisyUI。新的 MCP 工具、資源和 prompt 会自動添加。`,"We offer support via Discord. Join the daisyUI Discord and ask your questions there.":`我们通過 Discord 提供支持。加入 daisyUI Discord 并在那里提問。`,"Open Discord":`打開 Discord`,"Yes. You can cancel at any time from the order portal. You will keep access until the end of your billing cycle.":`是的。你可以隨時在訂單門戶取消。你会保留訪問權限直到計費周期結束。`,"Manage orders":`管理訂單`,"Digital products are not refundable. If there was a payment mistake, such as a duplicate payment, email us and we will help resolve it.":`數字產品不可退款。如果出現付款錯誤，例如重複付款，請給我们發郵件，我们会帮助解决。`,"Email help@daisyui.com":`發送郵件至 help@daisyui.com`,"Check your spam folder first. If you still can't find it, email help@daisyui.com.":`請先檢查垃圾郵件文件夹。如果仍然找不到，請發送郵件至 help@daisyui.com。`,"Email support":`聯系支持`,"Email help@daisyui.com and we will help you get the right package.":`發送郵件至 help@daisyui.com，我们会帮你獲得正確的套餐。`,"If the payment failed and you did not receive the product, try again. If money was deducted, it is usually refunded automatically within one or two weeks. Email help@daisyui.com if the issue persists.":`如果付款失败且你没有收到產品，請重試。如果已扣款，通常会在一到两周內自動退款。如果問題仍然存在，請發送郵件至 help@daisyui.com。`,"Step 2: Install Grok Build":`步驟2：安裝Grok Build`,"Install Grok Build if you haven't already.":`如果尚未安裝 Grok Build，請安裝。`,"Run this command to add the Blueprint MCP server. The `FIGMA` API key is optional and only needed for Figma-to-code conversion.":"執行此命令以新增 Blueprint MCP 伺服器。 `FIGMA` API 金鑰是可選的，僅在 Figma-to-code 轉換時需要。",'Check the connection with `grok mcp doctor daisyui-blueprint`. Read the <a href="https://docs.x.ai/build/features/mcp-servers" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Grok Build MCP docs</a> for project-scoped configuration and troubleshooting.':'檢查與 `grok mcp doctor daisyui-blueprint` 的連線。閱讀 <a href="https://docs.x.ai/build/features/mcp-servers" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Grok Build MCP 文件</a> 以了解專案範圍的配置和故障排除。',"MADE WITH BLUEPRINT MCP":`使用 Blueprint MCP 製作`,"LLMs often produce generic AI slop by default. They can skim skill files, ignore difficult instructions, hallucinate component syntax, and settle for mediocre design. You then spend more time, effort, and tokens asking for edits.":`預設情況下，LLMs 通常會產生通用 AI 斜率。他們可以瀏覽技能文件，忽略困難的指令，產生組件語法的幻覺，並滿足於平庸的設計。然後你會花更多的時間、精力和代幣來要求編輯。`,"Blueprint solves this with a guided MCP workflow. Six tools walk the LLM through the task, supply rules and resources one step at a time, and confirm the LLM understood them. The LLM then writes the code. A final inspection finds quality problems for the LLM to fix.":`Blueprint 透過指導 MCP 工作流程解決了這個問題。六種工具引導 LLM 完成任務，一次一步地提供規則和資源，並確認 LLM 理解它們。然後 LLM 寫入程式碼。最終檢查發現 LLM 有品質問題需要修復。`,"1. Setup Expert":`1. 設定專家`,"Provides project-specific setup resources:":`提供特定於專案的設定資源：`,"Framework and dependency information":`框架和依賴資訊`,"Tailwind CSS and daisyUI installation guidance":`Tailwind CSS 和 daisyUI 安裝指南`,"Configuration, themes, colors, fonts, icons, and file structure":`配置、主題、顏色、字體、圖示和文件結構`,"This helps the LLM work with your existing project instead of guessing its setup or adding conflicting configuration.":`這有助於 LLM 與您現有的項目配合使用，而不是猜測其設定或添加衝突的配置。`,"2. Rules Enforcer":`2. 規則執行者`,"Provides the complete daisyUI requirements for:":`提供完整的 daisyUI 要求：`,"Component implementation and syntax":`組件實作和語法`,"Accessibility and responsive behavior":`可訪問性和回應行為`,"Themes, media, and code quality":`主題、媒體和代碼品質`,"This keeps the LLM from skimming the rules or dropping constraints once it starts coding.":`這可以防止 LLM 在開始編碼後忽略規則或放棄約束。`,"3. Creative Director":`3.創意總監`,"Provides design guidance for:":`提供設計指導：`,"Product content, audience, and user experience":`產品內容、受眾和使用者體驗`,"Components, icons, images, design trends, and motion":`組件、圖標、圖像、設計趨勢和動作`,"This gives the LLM one clear visual direction. It avoids disconnected choices and familiar AI-generated layouts.":`這為 LLM 提供了一個清晰的視覺方向。它避免了斷開連接的選擇和熟悉的 AI 產生的佈局。`,"4. Page Architect":`4.頁面架構師`,"Provides a matching plan from 211 page architectures, including:":`提供211個頁面架構的配對方案，包括：`,"Page purpose, sections, content order, and user goals":`頁面用途、部分、內容順序和使用者目標`,"Actions, navigation, and component composition":`操作、導航和組件組合`,"Responsive behavior, interaction states, and edge cases":`響應行為、互動狀態和邊緣情況`,"This helps the LLM plan the full page before writing markup, including states a short prompt may leave out.":`這有助於 LLM 在編寫標記之前規劃整個頁面，包括簡短提示可能遺漏的狀態。`,"5. Component Syntax Expert":`5. 組件語法專家`,"Provides current daisyUI resources for each required component:":`為每個所需組件提供目前的 daisyUI 資源：`,"Correct structure and class names":`正確的結構和類別名`,"Variants, sizes, states, and modifiers":`變體、尺寸、狀態和修飾符`,"Rules, code snippets, and examples":`規則、程式碼片段和範例`,"This lets the LLM use maintained daisyUI syntax instead of recalling stale or invented classes from training data.":`這使得 LLM 使用維護的 daisyUI 語法，而不是從訓練資料中呼叫陳舊或發明的類別。`,"6. Quality Inspector":`6、質檢員`,"Checks the finished source for:":`檢查完成的原始碼：`,"daisyUI syntax and rule violations":`daisyUI 文法和規則違規`,"Visual hierarchy, spacing, density, and composition":`視覺層次、間距、密度與構圖`,"Accessibility, responsive behavior, themes, and missing states":`可訪問性、回應行為、主題和缺失狀態`,"This gives the LLM a specific repair list. The work finishes after the LLM fixes the reported issues and verifies the result.":`這為 LLM 提供了特定的維修清單。 LLM 修復報告的問題並驗證結果後，工作完成。`,"Design taste, originality, composition, color, and typography":`設計品味、原創性、構圖、色彩和版式`,"Get Blueprint MCP":`取得 Blueprint MCP`,"New and updated tools, prompts, and resources in daisyUI Blueprint v1.5.":`daisyUI Blueprint v1.5 中新增和更新的工具、提示和資源。`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Grok Build.":`為 Grok Build 安裝 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 伺服器。`,"See how six Blueprint MCP tools give your LLM the resources it needs to build better daisyUI interfaces.":`了解六種 Blueprint MCP 工具如何為您的 LLM 提供建立更好的 daisyUI 介面所需的資源。`};export{k as Architecture,i as Convert,C as Examples,A as GitMCP,b as Introducing,y as It,O as Mandatory,D as Prompts,_ as Providing,r as Randomize,h as Resources,E as Screenshot,t as Server,a as Size,g as Solution,e as Updates,u as Use,m as and,p as close,v as context,d as copied,f as copy,o as day,j as default,s as hour,c as min,w as read,l as sec,T as skipped,n as spacing,S as variables,x as variants};